      <h2 class="orgchart__tier-title" id="orgchart-state-title">State of Colorado</h2>
      <p class="orgchart__tier-intro">Statewide agencies whose authority reaches into El Paso County: the Attorney General's enforcement surface, the Civil Rights Division's parallel ADA filing path, the Bureau of Investigation's missing-persons system, the Department of Local Affairs (which holds the special-district registry under <strong>CRS Title 32</strong>), and the Department of Public Health &amp; Environment.</p>
