          <span class="orgchart__card-tag orgchart__card-tag--active">Active</span>
        </div>
        <p class="orgchart__card-role">State enforcement for consumer protection, antitrust, civil rights. Filed alongside DOJ in the RealPage algorithmic-pricing antitrust case.</p>
        <p class="orgchart__works-label">Work on this site</p>
