          <span class="orgchart__card-tag orgchart__card-tag--active">Active</span>
        </div>
        <p class="orgchart__card-role">State-level civil-rights and ADA enforcement. Parallel filing path to DOJ Civil Rights — file with one, both, or escalate from one to the other.</p>
