          <span class="orgchart__card-tag orgchart__card-tag--active">Active</span>
        </div>
        <p class="orgchart__card-role">Holds the statewide special-district registry under CRS Title 32. When a local metro district hides its records, DOLA is a parallel filing surface.</p>
