      <p class="orgchart__tier-intro">Five sub-groups: the County itself, the City of Colorado Springs, downtown taxing districts (BID/DDA/TIF), the 284 special districts billed to your property tax, and the regional bodies (PPROEM emergency operations) that span jurisdiction lines.</p>
